<http://drug.uk/dosage/df1724cf-b63c-4375-898e-32c635623cf7> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "2 mg/kg to be given over 24 hours." .
<http://drug.uk/dosage/df1724cf-b63c-4375-898e-32c635623cf7> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/Dosage> .
