<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/0284685e-1f55-4fbf-8756-8e94ccaf40c3> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Theoretical" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/0284685e-1f55-4fbf-8756-8e94ccaf40c3> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Severe" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/0284685e-1f55-4fbf-8756-8e94ccaf40c3> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Carbamazepine is predicted to decrease the efficacy of Fluconazole and Fluconazole increases the concentration of Carbamazepine. Manufacturer advises avoid or monitor Carbamazepine concentration and adjust dose accordingly.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/0284685e-1f55-4fbf-8756-8e94ccaf40c3> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/04440fbd-5e6d-47ca-8224-b6758ea8f1e8> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Study" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/04440fbd-5e6d-47ca-8224-b6758ea8f1e8> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Moderate" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/04440fbd-5e6d-47ca-8224-b6758ea8f1e8> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Carbamazepine decreases the exposure to Tiagabine. Manufacturer advises monitor and adjust Tiagabine dose.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/04440fbd-5e6d-47ca-8224-b6758ea8f1e8> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/04992e24-161e-4b67-9b19-2d132eaed136> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Theoretical" .
