<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/0a81d215-af82-4892-b9fc-414a479b19a9> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Anecdotal" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/0a81d215-af82-4892-b9fc-414a479b19a9> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Severe" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/0a81d215-af82-4892-b9fc-414a479b19a9> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Paracetamol has been reported to cause high anion gap metabolic acidosis when given with Flucloxacillin. Manufacturer advises caution.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/0a81d215-af82-4892-b9fc-414a479b19a9> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/19bc4ecf-ae50-4439-892f-8478eb8e4604> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Study" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/19bc4ecf-ae50-4439-892f-8478eb8e4604> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Moderate" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/19bc4ecf-ae50-4439-892f-8478eb8e4604> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Flucloxacillin (high-dose) might decrease the exposure to Tacrolimus. Manufacturer makes no recommendation.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/19bc4ecf-ae50-4439-892f-8478eb8e4604> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/212cf013-2e6c-415b-89a1-c0e417a562b9> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Anecdotal" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/212cf013-2e6c-415b-89a1-c0e417a562b9> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Severe" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/212cf013-2e6c-415b-89a1-c0e417a562b9> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Flucloxacillin is predicted to increase the risk of toxicity when given with Methotrexate. Manufacturer advises monitor.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/212cf013-2e6c-415b-89a1-c0e417a562b9> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/3aadce70-51f3-405f-a2fd-50ba2f745f6c> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Anecdotal" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/3aadce70-51f3-405f-a2fd-50ba2f745f6c> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Moderate" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/3aadce70-51f3-405f-a2fd-50ba2f745f6c> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Flucloxacillin (particularly high-dose) might greatly decrease the concentration of Isavuconazole. Manufacturer makes no recommendation.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/3aadce70-51f3-405f-a2fd-50ba2f745f6c> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/56edb439-1fae-4b9f-b2a7-17bec7dd0d72> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Anecdotal" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/56edb439-1fae-4b9f-b2a7-17bec7dd0d72> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Severe" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/56edb439-1fae-4b9f-b2a7-17bec7dd0d72> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Flucloxacillin potentially alters the anticoagulant effect of Acenocoumarol. Manufacturer advises monitor INR and adjust dose.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/56edb439-1fae-4b9f-b2a7-17bec7dd0d72> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/c1494a6b-26c3-4aa9-9ead-27d698aff72e> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Study" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/c1494a6b-26c3-4aa9-9ead-27d698aff72e> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Moderate" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/c1494a6b-26c3-4aa9-9ead-27d698aff72e> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Flucloxacillin (particularly high-dose) might greatly decrease the concentration of Posaconazole. Manufacturer makes no recommendation.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/c1494a6b-26c3-4aa9-9ead-27d698aff72e> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/d441e9fb-8f79-4115-a10a-b0c7eb00c20f> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Theoretical" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/d441e9fb-8f79-4115-a10a-b0c7eb00c20f> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Severe" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/d441e9fb-8f79-4115-a10a-b0c7eb00c20f> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Flucloxacillin is predicted to increase the risk of bleeding events when given with Phenindione. Manufacturer makes no recommendation.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/d441e9fb-8f79-4115-a10a-b0c7eb00c20f> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/daee9369-5aeb-4de1-b6dc-baa6c9b75466> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Study" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/daee9369-5aeb-4de1-b6dc-baa6c9b75466> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Moderate" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/daee9369-5aeb-4de1-b6dc-baa6c9b75466> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Flucloxacillin (particularly high-dose) might greatly decrease the concentration of Voriconazole. Manufacturer advises avoid or monitor.  " .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/daee9369-5aeb-4de1-b6dc-baa6c9b75466> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/InteractionDetail> .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/e662d6e4-ec64-4e27-845c-0d5a4e8db1f3> <http://drug.uk/model/evidence> "Study" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/e662d6e4-ec64-4e27-845c-0d5a4e8db1f3> <http://drug.uk/model/severity> "Moderate" .
<http://drug.uk/interaction/detail/e662d6e4-ec64-4e27-845c-0d5a4e8db1f3> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Flucloxacillin (high-dose) might decrease the exposure to Everolimus. Manufacturer makes no recommendation.  " .
